            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": ">   * Alternative: introduce `indentexpr=treesitter`\n\nI think this would make detecting indent type more straightforward, since it would have a different meaning at face value from indentexpr=\"\". It would also do less to disturb legacy behavior I'd think.",
